      <td width="84%" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><p>V&#7899;i m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh nh&agrave; cung c&#7845;p S&#7919;a ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u Vi&#7879;t Nam, b&#7857;ng nh&#7919;ng kinh nghi&#7879;m, ki&#7871;n th&#7913;c v&agrave; t&acirc;m huy&#7871;t ngh&#7873; nghi&#7879;p c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh BABY LOGO SHOP lu&ocirc;n l&#7855;ng nghe v&agrave; chia s&#7867; nh&#7919;ng y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u c&#361;ng nh&#432; b&#259;n kho&#259;n c&#7911;a c&aacute;c ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng v&#7873; s&#7919;a an to&agrave;n v&agrave; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a s&#7919;a. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u BABY LOGO SHOP d&#7921;a tr&ecirc;n s&#7921; h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng c&#7911;a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, cam k&#7871;t v&#7873; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng d&#7883;ch v&#7909;, ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch b&#7843;o v&#7879; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cho ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng v&agrave; s&#7921; &#273;a d&#7841;ng c&#7911;a c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i s&#7919;a ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng.<br />
      M&#7895;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng g&oacute;p m&#7863;t v&#7899;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ho&agrave;n h&#7843;o &#273;&#7871;n t&#7915;ng chi ti&#7871;t c&ograve;n l&agrave; th&agrave;nh qu&#7843; &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng nh&agrave; cung &#7913;ng nguy&ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&#7847;y t&acirc;m huy&#7871;t.
        </p>
        <p>-	Cung c&#7845;p s&#7919;a cho c&aacute;c nh&agrave; m&#7841;nh th&#432;&#7901;ng qu&acirc;n l&agrave;m t&#7915; thi&#7879;n v&#7899;i gi&aacute; t&#7889;t nh&#7845;t kh&ocirc;ng l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n.<br />
      BABY LOGO SHOP c&oacute; &#273;&#7897;i ng&#361; nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n nhi&#7879;t t&igrave;nh, n&#259;ng &#273;&#7897;ng, chu &#273;&aacute;o, c&oacute; ki&#7871;n th&#7913;c v&#7873; dinh d&#432;&#7905;ng, an to&agrave;n v&#7879; sinh th&#7921;c ph&#7849;m. BABY LOGO SHOP &#273;ang kh&ocirc;ng ng&#7915;ng t&#7921; ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n m&igrave;nh, ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&#7843; v&#7873; quy m&ocirc; m&#7841;ng l&#432;&#7899;i l&#7851;n ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m nh&#7857;m &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng m&#7885;i y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u c&#7911;a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.V&#7899;i s&#7921; &#7911;ng h&#7897; nhi&#7879;t th&agrave;nh c&#7911;a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng trong su&#7889;t th&#7901;i gian qua. BABY LOGO SHOP nh&#7853;n th&#7845;y c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i n&#7895; l&#7921;c h&#417;n n&#7919;a trong vi&#7879;c &#273;em &#273;&#7871;n cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng nh&#7919;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&oacute; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cao nh&#7845;t. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i mong mu&#7889;n nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n s&#7921; g&oacute;p &yacute; v&agrave; &#7911;ng h&#7897; t&#7915; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.C&#7843;m &#417;n kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng v&agrave; khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p &yacute; ki&#7871;n v&#7873; vi&#7879;c cung c&#7845;p s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#7911;a BABY LOGO SHOP</p></td>
